msgid "Spiritual Seekers and Mystics"
msgstr "Lorgaitheoirí Spiritúla agus Misticeacha"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Curious, introspective, open-minded, and drawn to "
"esoteric knowledge. They may have a strong interest in uncovering hidden "
"meanings or patterns in life. Occupations: Spiritual coaches, tarot readers,"
" astrologers, or individuals involved in New Age practices. Ideological "
"Spectrum: Likely to lean toward spiritual or metaphysical beliefs. They may "
"see the tools as a way to connect with deeper truths or universal energies."
msgstr ""
"Traidhes pearsantachta: Curárach, introspectif, sionartach, agus áirithe le "
"h-eolas esoteric. D'fhéadfadh sé bheith acu le tábhacht láidir ar mhíniú "
"rúnda nó patrúin i saol. Gníomhaíochtaí: Coachanna spiritúla, léitheoirí "
"tarot, astrolagóirí, nó daoine a bhuaileann i ngníomhaíochtaí New Age. "
"Spectrum eolaíoch: Is dócha go leanfaidh sé i dtaobh creideamh spiritúil nó "
"meta-fisiciúil. D'fhéadfadh sé leagadh ar na huirlisí mar bhealach chun "
"ceangal le fíorachtí níos doimhne nó le fuinneoga universal."

msgid "Numerologists and Gematria Enthusiasts"
msgstr "Númaraíochtóirí agus Enthusiast Gematria"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Analytical, detail-oriented, and fascinated by the "
"relationship between numbers and language. They may enjoy decoding symbolic "
"meanings. Occupations: Freelance numerologists, writers on esoteric topics, "
"or hobbyists exploring numerology. Ideological Spectrum: May range from "
"those who view numerology as a fun intellectual exercise to those who "
"believe in its profound spiritual significance."
msgstr ""
"Traidhes pearsantachta: Anailíseach, cáilithe le sonraí, agus spreagtha ag "
"na béartais idir na n-uimhreacha agus na teangacha. D'fhéadfadh siad "
"taitneamh a bhaint as deacrachtaí simbóil. Gníomhaíochtaí: Númaraíochtóirí "
"saoránach, scríbhneoirí ar ábhair esoteric, nó séascairí ag fiosrú "
"númaraíocht. Spectrum eolaíoch: Is féidir go bhfuil sé óna n-aire a "
"fhéachann ar númaraíocht mar ealaín intéireachtúil spraoi go dtí na n-aire a"
" bhfuil creideamh acu i bhfíordhúchán spiritúil aird."

msgid "Historians and Linguists"
msgstr "Stáireoirí agus Gaeltóirí"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Scholarly, methodical, and interested in historical or "
"cultural contexts of numerical systems like Abjad. Occupations: Academics, "
"researchers, or students studying Middle Eastern languages, history, or "
"religious texts. Ideological Spectrum: Likely to approach the tools from a "
"secular, academic perspective, focusing on their historical or linguistic "
"significance."
msgstr ""
"Traidhes pearsantachta: Leabharlann, ciallaithe, agus ag interest i "
"gcúiseanna stairiúla nó cultúrtha den chóras uimhreacha cosúil le Abjad. "
"Gníomhaíochtaí: Academics, researchers, nó mhic léinn ag léirmhíniú "
"teangacha na hÁise, stair, nó téacsanna muintir. Spectrum eolaíoch: Is dócha"
" go ndéanfad sé léirmhíniú ar na huirlisí ó thaobh aiseolas, le chéile le "
"stair nó teanga."

msgid "Religious or Faith-Based Individuals"
msgstr "Buidhneacha nó Fíoraíocht bunaithe ar Dhoine"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Devout, reflective, and seeking deeper connections to "
"their faith. They may use the tools to explore religious texts or divine "
"messages. Occupations: Religious scholars, imams, priests, or laypeople with"
" a strong interest in their faith’s mystical traditions. Ideological "
"Spectrum: Likely to have a traditional or conservative worldview, using the "
"tools to reinforce their spiritual beliefs."
msgstr ""
"Traidhes pearsantachta: Dúchúir, reflaxt, agus ag lorg ceangal níos doimhne "
"le creideamh. D'fhéadfadh siad na huirlisí a úsáid chun téacsanna muintir nó"
" teachtaireachtaí diocht a fhiosrú. Gníomhaíochtaí: Scholar muintir, imáim, "
"sacerdóit, nó foirne le tábhacht mhór ag tradúirí misticeacha creideamh. "
"Spectrum eolaíoch: Is dócha go bhfuil sé ina domhan fhiontraíoch nó "
"traidisiúnta, ag úsáid na huirlisí chun creideamh spiritúil a chumasú."

msgid "Writers and Artists"
msgstr "Scriobhair agus Ealaíontóirí"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Creative, imaginative, and drawn to symbolic or abstract"
" concepts. They may use the tools for inspiration or to add layers of "
"meaning to their work. Occupations: Authors, poets, visual artists, or "
"musicians. Ideological Spectrum: May range from secular creatives to those "
"with a spiritual or mystical bent."
msgstr ""
"Traidhes pearsantachta: Cruthaitheach, imníse, agus áirithe le conceptú "
"simbóil nó abstract. D'fhéadfadh siad na huirlisí a úsáid mar inspiortás nó "
"chun tús maith a chur le a n-obra. Gníomhaíochtaí: Údair, dhlíora, "
"ealaíontóirí infheicthe, nó muinínte. Spectrum eolaíoch: Is féidir go bhfuil"
" sé ó chruthaitheoirí secúla go dtí na n-aire a bhfuil buntáiste spiritúil "
"nó misticeach."

msgid "Puzzle and Riddle Enthusiasts"
msgstr "Enthusiast Puzzle agus Riddle"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Playful, intellectually curious, and enjoy solving "
"complex problems or decoding patterns. Occupations: Hobbyists, puzzle "
"designers, or educators. Ideological Spectrum: Likely to approach the tools "
"as a form of entertainment or mental exercise, with little ideological "
"attachment."
msgstr ""
"Traidhes pearsantachta: Spóirt, ag iarraidh intelleachtúil, agus ag baint "
"taitnimh as fuinneog mhór nó giniúint patrúin. Gníomhaíochtaí: Hobbyist, "
"dearbhálaí puzzlear, nó oiliúna. Spectrum eolaíoch: Is dócha go ndéanfaidh "
"sé léiriú ar na huirlisí mar bhall de bhall, le beagán aipeacht eolaíoch."

msgid "Conspiracy Theorists and Alternative Thinkers"
msgstr "Conspiracy Theorists agus Alternative Thinkers"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Skeptical of mainstream narratives, drawn to uncovering "
"hidden truths or patterns in systems. Occupations: Independent researchers, "
"bloggers, or activists. Ideological Spectrum: May have a more radical or "
"unconventional worldview, using the tools to support alternative theories or"
" narratives."
msgstr ""
"Traidhes pearsantachta: Skeptical of mainstream narratives, drawn to "
"uncovering hidden truths or patterns in systems. Gníomhaíochtaí: Taighdeoirí"
" anaonta, blogaireanna, nó gníomhairí. Spectrum eolaíoch: Is féidir a bheith"
" ag cur i dteanga an domhan níos radical nó neamhspleách, ag úsáid na "
"huirlisí chun teorainneacha nó nárúraí a thacaíocht a thabhairt."

